\* Autoupdate keywords (12-6-02)
  06 Dec 2002; Rodney Rees <manson@gentoo.org> changed sparc ~sparc keywords
 
*gnome-spell-0.5 (27 Sep 2002)

  10 Dec 2002; Jon Nall <nall@gentoo.org> gnome-spell-0.5.ebuild :
  added ~ppc to keywords

  06 Nov 2002; L. Boshell <leonardop@gentoo.org> : Added control-center-1.4
  dependency. Thanks to <suka_at@yahoo.de> for his report on bug #10254.
  
  27 Sep 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> :
  New version. Update to use gnome.org eclass.

*gnome-spell-0.4.1-r3 (17 Aug 2002)

  17 Aug 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org>
  gnome-spell-0.4.1-r3.ebuild files/digest-gnome-spell-0.4.1-r3 :

  Updated DEPEND to just contain aspell (in preparation for the new aspell
  release next week).

*gnome-spell-0.4.1-r2 (17 Jul 2002)
  17 Jul 2002; Gabriele Giorgetti <stroke@gentoo.org> gnome-spell-0.4.1-r2.ebuild :
  Updated dependence to ispell 3.2.06-r5 which added miscfiles to its dependencies.
  list. (fixed #5142).
   
*gnome-spell-1.0pre1 (10 Jun 2002)
  10 Jun 2002; Gabriele Giorgetti <stroke@gentoo.org> gnome-spell-1.0_pre1.ebuild :
  Looks like gnome-spell for gnome2 is pretty dead. So according with
  Spider I just removed its gnome2 related ebuilds.

*gnome-spell-1.0_pre1 (22 May 2002)
  22 May 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> gnome-spell-1.0_pre1.ebuild : 
  removed some faulty deps

*gnome-spell-1.0_pre1 (22 May 2002)
  22 May 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> gnome-spell-1.0_pre1.ebuild : 
  adding the pre release as well. 

  4 Apr 2002; M.Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> :

  Fix DEPEND to include bonobo, gal and libglade.  Drop gnome-core.

*gnome-spell-0.4.1-r1 (3 Apr 2002)

  3 Apr 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> gnome-spell-0.4.1-r1.ebuild :

  If nls is not in USE, then intl/libgettext needs to be touched for the 
  configure to work, otherwise it craps out.  Also, gnome-core is not an 
  absolute requirement, so I made it a gnome USE flag dependency instead.

*gnome-spell-0.4.1 (3 Apr 2002)

  3 Apr 2002; M.Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> :

  New gnome-spell package.  Libtoolize.

